                                "type": "text",
                                "text": "Hi developers, I would like to inform you that in version 2.9.2 of fuselibs the InterApp.launchUri - InterApp.launchApp API on iOS no longer works (iOS18).\n\nI needed to update the following line in the iOSInterop.uno file:\n\n-- [[UIApplication sharedApplication] openURL:[NSURL URLWithString:uri]];\n\n++ [[UIApplication sharedApplication] openURL:[NSURL URLWithString:uri] options:dict completionHandler:nil];\n\nI hope this helps."
